txt.en: 'The Corsairs know not what trouble they awaken, nor do I think they care. Their explorations of the tunnels beneath Emyn Ernil have awoken several beasts from the depths, deep-claws. Large lumbering creatures that, when awake, serve only to dig.\n\n'We cannot allow the tunnels to collapse from their work. The deep-claws must be stopped so we can continue to search and recover whatever of value is beneath. Head into the tunnels and defeat the creatures.'
The Corsair intrusion has awoken the deep-claws beneath Emyn Ernil, threatening the stability of the tunnels.
'I am sure there are more down there sleeping, waiting to be awoken. But for now, the tunnels should be safe.'
Emyn Ernil Tunnels - Claws of the Deep
Deep-claws are digging in the tunnels beneath Emyn Ernil.\n\nGelloth asked you to defeat the deep-claws that are threatening to collapse the tunnels beneath Emyn Ernil.
Gelloth can be found in Dol Amroth.\n\nGelloth will be very pleased to hear the tunnels are safe from collapse.
